{"tid":1834995,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港珠澳大橋周五起免通行費7天","createTime":"2020-01-22T15:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T16:24:45.000Z","uid":263196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c4a8744d040bab1d37fdb332733e6f5537a16c69","tid":1834995,"uid":263196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:56:21.000Z","msg":"運輸署今日(22日)宣布，根據港珠澳大橋管理局通知，由1月24日零時零分至1月30日午夜12時，大橋將一連7日實施小型客車免費通行政策。期間，小型客車經大橋收費站往返珠海或澳門口岸，不用繳付150元人民幣的通行費，而有關車輛行經電子收費車道及人工收費車道的行車安排維持不變。運輸署稱，小型客車是指七座位及以下，包括司機在內的載客車輛，即私家車及出租車。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大橋主橋位於內地水域，收費站亦位於內地範圍。根據屬地原則，負責營運大橋主橋的大橋管理局執行內地在農曆新年假期期間，免收小型客車通行費這項全國性政策。</span><br />\n運輸署發言人補充，如要駕駛私家車經大橋往返珠海或澳門，必須持有粵港澳政府發出的跨境私家車相關配額及牌證，或已辦理「大橋澳門口岸泊車轉乘計劃」的牌證及手續，包括已預約使用澳門口岸邊檢大樓東停車場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩感想？本來冇咩諗法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a66d9867d960002f1daad43760cfcf94ecbe293","tid":1834995,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:24:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">戴口罩 勤洗手 勤換口罩</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n1.24荔枝角收押所<br />\n1.27和你shop 彩虹戰衣</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uSBSm9r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuSBSm9r.jpg&h=fac8cfa1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2HMKXHM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2HMKXHM.png&h=a3a1e633&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OaZD19s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOaZD19s.jpg&h=065725f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">多聲援出庭手足<